Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libboost-all-dev, ros-rolling-angles, ros-rolling-geometry-msgs, ros-rolling-interactive-markers, ros-rolling-pluginlib, ros-rolling-rclcpp, ros-rolling-rviz-common, ros-rolling-rviz-default-plugins, ros-rolling-std-msgs, ros-rolling-tf2, ros-rolling-tf2-geometry-msgs, ros-rolling-tf2-ros, ros-rolling-visualization-msgs, ros-rolling-ros-workspace
Description: This package provides a gui program as well as a rviz plugin to publish static transforms.
 Both support the transformation between various Euler angle representations. The rviz plugin also allows to configure the transform with an interactive marker.
